---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

const updated = 'June 17, 2026';
const CONTACT = 'hello@spykeautomation.com';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — Spyke Automation"
  description="How Spyke Automation collects, uses, and protects information from visitors to spykeautomation.com."
>
  <Nav />
  <main class="legal">
    <div class="wrap">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="updated">Last updated: {updated}</p>

      <p class="lead">
        This policy explains what information Spyke Automation ("we", "us") collects through
        <strong>spykeautomation.com</strong>, why we collect it, and the choices you have. We keep
        data collection to the minimum needed to run an early-access program and improve the site.
      </p>

      <h2>Information we collect</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Information you give us.</strong> When you request early access, we collect the
          email address you submit. If you email us, we keep your message and contact details so we
          can reply.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Basic usage data.</strong> Like most websites, our hosting and any analytics may
          record standard technical information such as your IP address, browser type, and the pages
          you view. We use this in aggregate to understand traffic and improve the site.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How we use information</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>To contact you about early access and product availability.</li>
        <li>To respond to your questions and support requests.</li>
        <li>To operate, secure, and improve the website.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How we share information</h2>
      <p>
        We do <strong>not</strong> sell your personal information. We share it only with service
        providers that help us run the site and our early-access program (for example, form,
        email, and hosting providers), and only as needed to provide those services. We may also
        disclose information if required by law.
      </p>

      <h2>Data retention</h2>
      <p>
        We keep early-access emails until you ask us to remove them or until we no longer need them
        for the program. You can request deletion at any time using the contact details below.
      </p>

      <h2>Your choices</h2>
      <p>
        You can ask us to access, correct, or delete the personal information we hold about you, or
        to stop contacting you, by emailing <a href={`mailto:${CONTACT}`}>{CONTACT}</a>. Any
        product update emails will also include a way to opt out.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this policy as the product evolves. When we do, we will revise the "Last
        updated" date above. Material changes will be highlighted on this page.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about this policy? Email <a href={`mailto:${CONTACT}`}>{CONTACT}</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
